description: Overview* This high quality VGA splitter cable is for splitting a VGA signal to 2 VGA monitors, and provides an inexpensive solution for displaying a mirror image on 2 monitors (that use standard 15 pin plugs) at the same time.* Perfect for laptops to display on a separate, larger monitor.Technical Specifications* Connectors: 1x HD15 Male; 2x HD15 Female* Resolutions: Supports up to UXGA (1600x1200), WXGA (1680x1050), and HD 1080p (1920x1080)* Jacket: PVC* Shielding: Double Shielded Cable to Eliminate Interferences* RoHS Compliance: YesImportant Note* This is a splitter cable. You can only connect one source device (e.g. PC) to two display devices (e.g. monitor or projector).* This is a passive cable. It only duplicates the PC screen to monitor. It does NOTextend your PC to monitor
title: Cable Matters VGA Monitor Y Splitter 1 Foot
